entries.arrived_at_delivery: The Lambda shuttle is on it's way now. Stand by until it has arrived at your location.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: We have the data from the rebel officer. Command is very excited to get their hands on this information.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Beginning docking procedures in order to get the Rebel officer's data.
entries.failed_destroyed: You allowed your transfer shuttle to be destroyed? That was an expensive ship. You are going to have to answer to your commander about this failure.
entries.found_loc_d: Meet the shuttle at this location. Transfer the data immediately on it's arrival.
entries.hello_d: I understand that you have something that HQ is very interested in taking a look at.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Once the shuttle has arrived, target it and press the 'U' key in order to transfer the plans. Be on the look out for Rebel fighters who will probably attempt to stop this delivery from happening.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Yavin system and deliver the joint operations plan to the Imperial Lambda Shuttle. You will receive a navigation waypoint to the arrival location of the shuttle. Travel to this location and wait for the shuttle to arrive.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: When you arrive at the navigation waypoint to the Lambda shuttle, wait for it to arrive.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_t: Wait for the Arrival of the Lambda Shuttle
entries.split_quest_alert: High command also wants a live body to confirm the rebel officer's data. You are going to have to capture a rebel officer and bring him back to HQ alive.
entries.title: Yavin System: Deliver the Rebel Data
entries.title_d: Remain in the Yavin system and deliver the joint operations plan. You will receive a navigation waypoint to a shuttle that will pick up the joint operations plan from you. Travel to this navigation waypoint and wait for the shuttle to arrive. Once the shuttle arrives, press the 'U' key to dock with the shuttle targeted to transfer the plans. Enemy fighters will attempt to stop this delivery from taking place. You must keep yourself, as well as, the shuttle alive until you can complete the delivery.
